description.displayText: Jourdan has phenomenal for us during the remote learning period and we are really sad to lose her to her new job.  She's punctual, detail-oriented, responsible and great with the kids.  I highly recommend her for any family out there.

description.displayText:
I honestly don't even know where to begin because I couldn't of imagined raising three young children without her. Jourdan was always extremely punctual, and would arrive fully prepared and before her start time even when asked to arrive at odd hours. 
Jourdan is balanced, helpful, nurturing, playful, funny, agreeable, intelligent, and responsible. The characteristic that I admired most about her was her calm personality. Raising children can be stressful at times, and I learned a lot by watching her patiently care for our three children. She was one of the best parenting decisions I ever made, and I am confident that she had a positive effect on our children's lives.
She is loved and missed by our family.
